---
// Product section component showcasing key offerings
---

<section class="bg-brand-dark text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-[165px]">
    <!-- Two Column Header -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-16">
      <!-- Left Column - Content -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl uppercase mb-4"
          style="line-height: 110%; letter-spacing: 6px;"
        >
          HOW WE DELIVER
        </p>
        <h2
          class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl mb-6"
          style="line-height: 95%; font-weight: var(--font-weight-black);"
        >
          Sparq's AI-enabled product engineering system
        </h2>
        <p class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-80">
          Sparq blends AI-native product workflows with proven execution
          systems. Whether you're modernizing legacy platforms or building
          net-new experiences, we accelerate outcomes through modular,
          data-driven engagements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Placeholder Box -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="p-8 w-full" style="background-color: #16110F;">
          <img src="./images/sparq-methodology.svg" alt="" srcset="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Product Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-end">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <img
          src="/images/check.png"
          alt="Check Icon"
          class="w-[60px] h-[60px] mb-2"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold">
          AI-Accelerated discovery
        </h3>
        <p class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-80">
          Align signals + capacity plans
        </p>
        <p class="text-white hover:no-underline mt-auto">
          Helped a financial service provider reduce call volume by 30% and save
          $5.4m annually.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <img
          src="/images/check.png"
          alt="Check Icon"
          class="w-[60px] h-[60px] mb-2"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold">
          MVP in half the time
        </h3>
        <p class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-80">
          Co-pilot dev + validation sprints
        </p>
        <p class="text-white hover:no-underline mt-auto">
          Enabled a 33% faster market entry for a national healthcare network.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <img
          src="/images/check.png"
          alt="Check Icon"
          class="w-[60px] h-[60px] mb-2"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold">
          Continuous impact
        </h3>
        <p class="text-md md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl opacity-80">
          Live metrics + adaptive ops
        </p>
        <p class="text-white hover:no-underline mt-auto">
          Drove 150% reduction in bag validation time and 100% compliance
          accuracy for a US stadium.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
